This page documents '''enemy data''' in '''[[Soul Blazer]]''' (SNES).

==Overview==
Soul Blazer features '''64 unique enemy types''' across 7 acts (6 main areas + World of Evil).
Enemies spawn from '''Soul Lairs''' which must be destroyed to release trapped souls.

Total enemy count:
* Regular enemies: 48
* Mini-bosses: 9
* Act bosses: 6
* Final boss (Deathtoll): 1

