==Enemy Mechanics==

===Combat Formula===
<pre>
Base Damage = (Player_ATK × Sword_Multiplier) - Enemy_DEF
If Base_Damage < 1, Base_Damage = 1

Final Damage Modifiers:
- Critical Hit (1/16 chance): Damage × 2
- Elemental weakness: Damage × 1.5
- Elemental resistance: Damage × 0.5
- Wrong sword type: Damage = 0 (Metal/Ghost enemies)
</pre>

===Experience Scaling===
{| class="wikitable"
! Level Range !! EXP Multiplier !! Notes
|-
| 1-5 || 100% || Full experience
|-
| 6-10 || 75% || Slight reduction
|-
| 11-15 || 50% || Half experience
|-
| 16-20 || 25% || Quarter experience
|-
| 21-25 || 10% || Minimal experience
|}

Maximum level is 25. Experience from enemies more than 10 levels below player is reduced to 1.

===GEM Drops===
GEMs have a variable drop rate:
* Base drop: 100%
* Bonus GEMs (1/8 chance): Drop amount × 2
* GEM Doubler magic: All drops × 2

